{"type":"message","id":"5b233a83","parentId":"80eee7cf","timestamp":"2026-03-06T15:47:35.789Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's truncated but we see the sub-agent is still early in the process. It's reading files and planning. This may take a while. Since the sub-agent is running with a run timeout (default maybe 600 seconds). We should wait longer. Let's do something else: we can also examine the workspace-janitor skill to see how it uses cron. Let's see its SKILL.md to understand cron integration. But we can also just wait.\n\nLet's check the time: 10:44 AM. The sub-agent started at 10:40. It's been 4 minutes. It could take 30 minutes. We'll wait.\n\nWe can also think about the cron job addition. Let's see the syntax for adding a cron job. We can run `openclaw cron add --help`. Let's do that:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_XGcxxaEi5CzNkF2ghKcXCgTq","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --help 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":3642,"output":399,"cacheRead":42112,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46153,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772812044050}}
{"type":"message","id":"4aef28c6","parentId":"5b233a83","timestamp":"2026-03-06T15:47:37.168Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_XGcxxaEi5CzNkF2ghKcXCgTq","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.2 (85377a2) — Greetings, Professor Falken\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1348,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.2 (85377a2) — Greetings, Professor Falken\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772812057159}}
