{"type":"message","id":"377fca0a","parentId":"92348a71","timestamp":"2026-03-06T16:00:27.609Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_8JVT103wwuAK8bpzGUS2QOCw","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Reconciliation started at 2026-03-06 11:00:27\nReconciliation ended at 2026-03-06 11:00:27 (duration: 0.0s)\nFound 8 unique Pattern‑Keys in ERRORS.md\nFound 14 Pattern‑Keys in INDEX.md\n✅ All ERRORS.md keys present in INDEX.md\n⚠️  2 Pattern‑Keys missing from LEARNINGS.md (no learning extracted):\n   - runtime|STALL|model|no_response\n   - test|DUPLICATE|test|test|test\n⚠️  1 high‑severity incidents without guardrails:\n   - runtime|STALL|model|no_response (severity=S2)\n\n🔁 Running update_index.py to refresh INDEX.md and REPORT.md...\n✅ Index updated\n## Reconciliation Summary (2026-03-06 11:00:27)\n\n- Total incidents in ERRORS.md: 8\n- Missing from INDEX.md: 0\n- Missing from LEARNINGS.md: 2\n- Repeated incidents without guardrails: 0\n- High‑severity incidents without guardrails: 1\n\nReconciliation completed successfully."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":88,"aggregated":"Reconciliation started at 2026-03-06 11:00:27\nReconciliation ended at 2026-03-06 11:00:27 (duration: 0.0s)\nFound 8 unique Pattern‑Keys in ERRORS.md\nFound 14 Pattern‑Keys in INDEX.md\n✅ All ERRORS.md keys present in INDEX.md\n⚠️  2 Pattern‑Keys missing from LEARNINGS.md (no learning extracted):\n   - runtime|STALL|model|no_response\n   - test|DUPLICATE|test|test|test\n⚠️  1 high‑severity incidents without guardrails:\n   - runtime|STALL|model|no_response (severity=S2)\n\n🔁 Running update_index.py to refresh INDEX.md and REPORT.md...\n✅ Index updated\n## Reconciliation Summary (2026-03-06 11:00:27)\n\n- Total incidents in ERRORS.md: 8\n- Missing from INDEX.md: 0\n- Missing from LEARNINGS.md: 2\n- Repeated incidents without guardrails: 0\n- High‑severity incidents without guardrails: 1\n\nReconciliation completed successfully.","cwd":"/home/open