econciliation_runner.py` – wrapper for scheduled runs with logging\n   - `update_index.py` – refactored to use the common module\n   - `SKILL.md` – updated with full automation docs, integration examples, cron setup, and extended Pattern‑Key coverage.\n\n3. **Cron job installed** – runs Monday–Friday at 1:30 PM Panama Time, already validated.\n\n4. **Validation passed** – incident emission, index rebuild, reconciliation scanner, and Handoff Report parsing all work as expected.\n\n## 🚀 System Status\nThe `error‑learning‑loop` skill now:\n- Captures incidents automatically from sub‑agent handoffs, watchdog stalls, and skill‑written errors.\n- Guarantees no orphan incidents via daily reconciliation.\n- Promotes guardrails when patterns repeat or severity is high.\n- Requires zero manual intervention for routine learning.\n\n**Next step**: Integrate `emit_incident` into `agent‑watchdog` and other skills to complete the event‑driven chain. The cron backup will already start its daily checks today."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":64023,"output":849,"cacheRead":3072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67944,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772813173556}}
