{"type":"message","id":"79b7243b","parentId":"dc28e32d","timestamp":"2026-03-06T16:21:52.116Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All three still active (updatedAt recent). I'll provide a progress update now, mentioning that cron job is installed and integration is distributed across sub-agents, with one completed. I'll also mention that I'm monitoring the others. Use normal assistant voice. Let's also update memory. First, add a note about the completed sub-agent. Then respond.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_B2HXsodIjJmumXnBI6JHkBRR","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-06.md","oldText":"Tested emit_incident: works, triggers learning loop automatically.\n\nTested reconciliation script: works, updates INDEX.md.\n\nAdded system cron job (crontab) for daily reconciliation Monday–Friday at 1:30 PM Panama Time.\n\nEvent-driven layer is operational; watchdog already integrated with learning loop. Need to integrate other skills with emit_incident.\n\nAwaiting sub-agent handoff report.","newText":"Tested emit_incident: works, triggers learning loop automatically.\n\nTested reconciliation script: works, updates INDEX.md.\n\nAdded system cron job (crontab) for daily reconciliation Monday–Friday at 1:30 PM Panama Time.\n\nEvent-driven layer is operational; watchdog already integrated with learning loop. Need to integrate other skills with emit_incident.\n\nSpawned sub-agents for integrating emit_incident into critical skills:\n1. agent-watchdog (running) – watchdog-integrate-emit-incident\n2. salesforce-architect (completed) – integration successful, utils_io.py updated\n3. salesforce-code-auditor (running)\n4. long-prompt-orchestrator (running)\n\nAll sub-agents registered with watchdog for monitoring.\n\nAwaiting remaining handoff reports."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":1898,"out