{"type":"message","id":"b831c90b","parentId":"6df263d4","timestamp":"2026-03-06T16:35:42.306Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_3sQMVOyKBnvh9UZpk181SVSA","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.2 (85377a2) — I'm not AI-powered, I'm AI-possessed. Big difference.\n\nUsage: openclaw config [options] [command]\n\nNon-interactive config helpers (get/set/unset/file/validate). Run without\nsubcommand for the setup wizard.\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help           Display help for command\n  --section <section>  Configure wizard sections (repeatable). Use with no\n                       subcommand. (default: [])\n\nCommands:\n  file                 Print the active config file path\n  get                  Get a config value by dot path\n  set                  Set a config value by dot path\n  unset                Remove a config value by dot path\n  validate             Validate the current config against the schema without\n                       starting the gateway"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1253,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.2 (85377a2) — I'm not AI-powered, I'm AI-possessed. Big difference.\n\nUsage: openclaw config [options] [command]\n\nNon-interactive config helpers (get/set/unset/file/validate). Run without\nsubcommand for the setup wizard.\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help           Display help for command\n  --section <section>  Configure wizard sections (repeatable). Use with no\n                       subcommand. (default: [])\n\nCommands:\n  file                 Print the active config file path\n  get                  Get a config value by dot path\n  set                  Set a config value by dot path\n  unset                Remove a config value by dot path\n  validate             Validate the current config against the schema without\n                       starting the gateway","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772814942301}}
