{"type":"message","id":"1b26c4e7","parentId":"3fcb5f47","timestamp":"2026-03-06T16:53:06.663Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No veo el inicio del array. Necesito buscar desde el inicio del proveedor. Mejor escribir un script Python para modificar de manera segura. Pero podemos hacerlo con edit si somos cuidadosos.\n\nPrimero, eliminar google. Luego agregar deepseek-chat. Luego cambiar primario a deepseek-chat.\n\nVoy a escribir un script Python pequeño y ejecutarlo. Es más limpio. Usaré write para crear un script y ejecutarlo. Primero, hacer backup. Ya hay backup. Ahora script.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_DDaViEqpNSkt16C96NPaR6gq","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/configure_deepseek.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nimport json\nimport sys\n\nconfig_path = \"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/openclaw.json\"\nwith open(config_path, 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# 1. Remove google provider from models.providers\nif \"models\" in config and \"providers\" in config[\"models\"]:\n    config[\"models\"][\"providers\"].pop(\"google\", None)\n\n# 2. Add deepseek-chat model to custom-api-deepseek-com provider\ndeepseek_provider = config[\"models\"][\"providers\"][\"custom-api-deepseek-com\"]\ndeepseek_chat = {\n    \"id\": \"deepseek-chat\",\n    \"name\": \"deepseek-chat (Chat)\",\n    \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n    \"reasoning\": False,\n    \"input\": [\"text\"],\n    \"cost\": {\n        \"input\": 0,\n        \"output\": 0,\n        \"cacheRead\": 0,\n        \"cacheWrite\": 0\n    },\n    \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n    \"maxTokens\": 128000\n}\ndeepseek_provider[\"models\"].append(deepseek_chat)\n\n# 3. Set deepseek-chat as primary default model\nif \"agents\" not in config:\n    config[\"agents\"] = {}\nif \"defaults\" not in config[\"agents\"]:\n    config[\"agents\"][\"defaults\"] = {}\nif \"model\" not in config[\"agents\"][\"defaults\"]:\n    config[\"agents\"][\"defaults\"][\"model\"] = {}\n\nconfig[\"agents\"][\"defaults\"][\"model\"][\"primary\"] = \"custom-api-deepseek-com/deepseek-chat\"\nconfig[\"agents\"][\"defaults\"][\"model\"][\"fallbacks\"] = [\"custom-api-deepseek-com/deepseek-reasoner\"]\n\n# 4. Add aliases for clarity\nif \"models\" not in config[\"agents\"][\"defaults\"]:\n    config[\"agents\"][\"defaults\"][\"models\"] = {}\nconfig[\"agents\"][\"defaults\"][\"models\"][\"custom-api-deepseek-com/deepseek-chat\"] = {\"alias\": \"DeepSeek\"}\nconfig[\"agents\"][\"defaults\"][\"models\"][\"custom-api-deepseek-com/deepseek-reasoner\"] = {\"alias\": \"DeepSeek-Reasoner\"}\n\n# Write back\nwith open(config_path, 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2)\n    f.write(\"\\n\")\n\nprint(\"Configuration updated:\")\nprint(\"- Google provider removed (only embeddings remain via memorySearch)\")\nprint(\"- deepseek-chat model added\")\nprint(\"- Primary model set to deepseek-chat, fallback to deepseek-reasoner\")\nprint(\"- Aliases: DeepSeek (chat), DeepSeek-Reasoner (reasoner)\")"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":51323,"output":886,"cacheRead":29312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81521,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772815946257}}
